label.value: a glycerol dibiphytanyl glycerol tetraether phospholipid(2-)

definition.value: A spiro compound that is 1,8-dimethyl-4-(prop-1-en-2-yl)spiro[4.5]decane that has been dehydrogenated to introduce a double bond at position 8-9 (the 1R,4R,5S isomer).
A 3alpha-hydroxy steroid that is androst-5-ene carrying three additional hydroxy groups at positions 3alpha, 16beta and 17beta.
